divs: Sighting DetailsAfter the light faded..we kept staring at the sky for like 10 or 15 minutes, and were actually a little freaked out with the amount of airplanes that were all over the sky. We must have counted like 7 planes all in one area..and like 4 planes in another area..and also random planes just everywhere! Some looked close, most looked far. The planes were a bright blinking light with 2 big red lights. Very strange and weird feeling.
